{"tid":1168731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國學者估計貿易戰到侵侵落台都唔會停止，最少要打到「習近平退休」","createTime":"2019-05-24T01:30:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T14:00:42.000Z","uid":155095,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"80ba0c7afb20b776278c7b8964027ac401fdb80c","tid":1168731,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T01:30:15.000Z","msg":"【中美貿易戰】<ins>學者預測：打到2035年 未來兩年矛盾激化</ins><br />\n<br />\n中國國際經濟交流中心首席研究員<ins>張燕生</ins>預測指，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>中美貿易戰</strong>將持續到2035年</span>，其間雙方將處於「爭吵和對話」的循環中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://thenilewires.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/trump-xi-us-china-boxing-2x1-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthenilewires.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2Ftrump-xi-us-china-boxing-2x1-1.jpg&h=0d99ea88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n張燕生並估計，中美間紛爭<span style=\"color: red;\">最激烈的時刻應是2021年至2025年間</span>，屆時兩國在經濟、貿易、技術、金融等領域內將發生各種摩擦。 <br />\n<br />\n不過，張燕生沒有解釋如何算出這些年份。有指，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2035年</strong>，中共總書記<strong>習近平</strong>將是<strong>82歲</strong></span>，有可能已經退下。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/xi-forever.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2Fxi-forever.jpg&h=c961bcb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n張燕生說：「未來幾年，中美雙方將考驗彼此的戰略意圖，並且極有可能對彼此產生誤判導致貿易協商更加艱難。」根據他的預測，中美貿易戰可分為以下3個階段：<br />\n<br />\n第1階段：<br />\n在<strong>2020年之前</strong>，中美仍處於互相試探的狀態，很容易發生誤判；<br />\n<br />\n第2階段： <br />\n發生在<strong>2021至2025年</strong>，兩國將在經濟、貿易、科技、金融等方面發生摩擦，是雙方經貿關係最困難的一段時間；<br />\n<br />\n第3階段：<br />\n<strong>2026至2035年</strong>，中美將從非理性對抗，逐步走向理性合作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/26170801/adsfgsdgageweg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F26170801%2Fadsfgsdgageweg.png&h=d8965e88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/04155238/asdfafwegasdfawefgawefds.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F04155238%2Fasdfafwegasdfawefgawefds.png&h=91b98bdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n張燕生預期，貿易戰會促使從事製造業的外商撤離中國，而中國則會極力保留高端科技產業，另外更多現代服務業會會進入內地市場，<span style=\"color: red;\">美國將來或會反過來，依賴中國的高端產業鏈</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/u44112EatShitv106.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fu44112EatShitv106.jpg&h=d2b796fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190523&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=59633886\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190523%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D59633886&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhGvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=8f5614c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190523%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D59633886&h=98cd416e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190523&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=59633886</a>"},{"pid":"460df304fff25786fcd4ec5791293821208a04a2","tid":1168731,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T01:32:22.000Z","msg":"我估計仲準過呢班垃圾黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28cf0383ef7312488137b94801d6845e7dd7e5f","tid":1168731,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T01:32:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d2f3d19faa7ed604dabdbe644d96d068f26cc5c","tid":1168731,"uid":92603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T01:39:02.000Z","msg":"蘋果真係連依d柒野都報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97b9abc955517c9b2f07e0ba2